    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's in absolutely stunning condition inside and out. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s basically a brand-new car without the brand-new price tag! If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and pampered, this is the one. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
