    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a collector-grade specimen that presents in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, retaining its original new-car scent with absolutely no wear on the leather bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic component functions with factory precision, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. Accompanied by a full binder of meticulous service records and two sets of keys, this vehicle has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of peerless distinction. This specimen has been curated to an uncompromising standard, exhibiting an aesthetic and mechanical state that mirrors its original factory delivery. Every surface, from the refined interior appointments to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a legacy of meticulous stewardship. This is an acquisition for the discerning driver who demands an investment-grade vehicle in absolute showroom condition. We invite you to experience a motorcar that transcends the standard pre-owned market.",
      "price": 46500.0,
