    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve totally babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
