      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having received a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement using high-tensile ARP bolts. The subframe has been structurally reinforced to mitigate common E46 floor-pan fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission operates with crisp engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The suspension retains factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is felt in every corner. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and zero track use.",
